Constructor Detail

Raumklima

public Raumklima()
the standard constructor (without the optional values of the second Constructor, which is only needed in order to make the numbering in the Title of the MainWindow work. This Constructor just calls the setup() Method.

Raumklima

public Raumklima(int newTitleNumber,
                 Raumklima newPrevious,
                 Raumklima newNext)
the Secondary Constructor, which includes the "advanced" features (for the numbering scheme). This Constructor just calls the setup() Method.

Parameters:
newTitleNumber - the number that should be displayed in the Titlebar on the MainWindow
newPrevious - the preceding instance of Raumklima (only used to update the numbering scheme if a window is closed or opened)
newNext - the following instance of Raumklima (only used to update the numbering scheme if a window is closed or opened)
